{"tid":1587472,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"小巴車牌NY3831 司機報警，至少8名手足被捕。","createTime":"2019-09-22T11:53:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T17:10:51.000Z","uid":294825,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"beee00d52e4316b75d3ff7c75daafc947401eb66","tid":1587472,"uid":294825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T11:53:04.000Z","msg":"【1850】秀茂坪疑有紅van司機報警，成車人被扣查，可能全部乘客皆將被捕。車牌NY3831。<br />\n<br />\n另外，所有車輛都有機會被搜，包括綠van。現城隧有警察set左Rb，以下幾條綠van線皆經城隧，大家小心：481, 481A, 481B, 403, 403X。<br />\n<br />\n【1917】沙田城門隧道，向荃灣出口有警截查巴士，巴士上乘客樣貌被錄影。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7KcUwyH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7KcUwyH.jpg&h=2529890d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"77b7cb862db55fc9363a9ae771d8d5944cfd2d3a","tid":1587472,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T11:54:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a2fa466c6b85b091484ca43afa963c912f894e01","tid":1587472,"uid":203889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T11:55:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71bb957d02950f6956eadaecbc2a9a6d14c6f0db","tid":1587472,"uid":85578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T11:55:23.000Z","msg":"屌你"},{"pid":"93c95447b1cfc76dcb5f0f026eb73b326546f8ad","tid":1587472,"uid":76609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T11:55:48.000Z","msg":"估唔到有人信紅VAN"},{"pid":"3f0b74174dd03ffb366571e48aab6ed92bc5d8db","tid":1587472,"uid":38182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T11:56:56.000Z","msg":"鶳"},{"pid":"8834fb9dc91e65c6f962f5c506e220f4d80933ba","tid":1587472,"uid":71140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T12:00:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"21e1edf7428cb06a